Class Processor

java.lang.Object
icyllis.arc3d.engine.trash.Processor
Direct Known Subclasses:
TransferProcessor
@Deprecated @Immutable public abstract class Processor extends Object
Deprecated.
Provides custom shader code to the Arc3D shading pipeline. Processor objects must be immutable: after being constructed, their fields may not change.
